name: The Red Bird Miniature Golden Locket Earrings
description:
The Red Bird Miniature Golden Locket earrings feature beautiful red sparrows on 10mm sanded brass lockets hung from nickle-free gold-plated brass ear wires. Each locket earring is fully functional and ready for your pictures. These earrings are uniquely wonderful and will quickly become your new favorite pair of earrings. Each sparrow is made using my own unique patina painting process and are sealed with a non-toxic glaze. No two pair of earrings are exactly the same. Thank you for supporting an urban artist and buying handmade all in one purchase.

Earring specifications:
The ear wires are made from 20g nickle-free gold-plated brass wire
Earring size : the lockets are 10mm. The earrings are just under 1" long.

All items come gift boxed and ready to give or keep.

The rattle snake is a mixture of browns, black and tans with yellowish eyes and an devilish smirk. This little snake is definitely up to no good. This necklace shows off your wild side! Thank you for supporting an urban artist and buying handmade all in one purchase.
